%% ============================================
%% FRONTISPIECE — "全書一句話" spread built on Mark's
%% own opening sentence (1:1), the book's self-declared
%% thesis, not a borrowed framework verse.
%% ============================================
\thispagestyle{empty}
\begin{center}
\vspace*{0.3in}

\begin{tikzpicture}
  \draw[ScriptureGold, line width=0.8pt] (-2.8,0) -- (-0.55,0);
  \fill[ScriptureGold] (0,0) circle (0.055);
  \draw[ScriptureGold, line width=0.8pt] (0.55,0) -- (2.8,0);
\end{tikzpicture}

\vspace{0.22cm}
{\Large\bfseries\color{ChapterRed} 全書一句話 \textperiodcentered\ The Whole Book in One Sentence}

\vspace{0.30cm}
\fcolorbox{ScriptureGold}{ScriptureBg}{%
\begin{minipage}{4.6in}
\centering\vspace{0.2cm}
\normalsize\color{CommentaryBrown}
\textbf{\color{JesusRed}神的兒子}，耶穌基督福音的起頭。\\[0.5em]
\footnotesize\itshape
The beginning of the gospel of Jesus Christ, the \textbf{\color{JesusRed}Son of God}.\\[0.4em]
\small\color{ChapterRed} 馬可福音 1:1 \textperiodcentered\ Mark 1:1
\vspace{0.2cm}
\end{minipage}}

\vspace{0.35cm}
{\small\color{TextGray} 不是「立刻」，是「兒子」——全書的鑰匙在第一句話裏\\
\textit{Not ``immediately'' — ``Son.'' The key to the whole book is in the first sentence.}}

\vspace{0.30cm}
{\small
\renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.3}
\begin{tabular}{@{}p{1.8cm}p{2.6cm}p{4.6cm}@{}}
\toprule
\textbf{身分} & \textbf{階段} & \textbf{在全書的展開} \\
\midrule
兒子 Son & 蒙愛、受印證 & 1:1-11 —— 先是兒子，蒙父所愛，然後才差遣 \\
僕人 Servant & 捨己、服事到底 & 1:14-16:20 —— 因為是兒子，才甘心作僕人；10:45 是這身分活出來的樣式 \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
}

\vspace{0.4cm}
\textcolor{ScriptureGold}{\rule{2.5in}{0.7pt}}
\vspace{0.3cm}

{\bfseries\color{ChapterRed} 讀經之鑰 \textperiodcentered\ How to Read This Book}

\vspace{0.18cm}
\begin{minipage}{4.6in}
\small\color{TextGray}
先做兒子，才能作僕人——摩西是神家中的僕人，耶穌卻是神家中的兒子（來3:5-6）。\\
若你只記得馬可「立刻」的急促節奏，這卷書只讀懂了一半；\\
先看見第一句話的「兒子」，才能看懂後面每一次「服事」的分量。\\[0.5em]
\textit{\footnotesize
Moses was a servant in God's house; Christ is a Son over God's house (Heb 3:5-6).\\
If all you remember is Mark's breathless ``immediately,'' you have only read half the book.\\
See the ``Son'' in the first sentence first — then every act of service that follows will carry its true weight.}
\end{minipage}

\vfill
{\scriptsize\color{LightGray} PubHub 三書精讀系統 \textperiodcentered\ Soli Deo Gloria}

\vspace{0.3in}
\end{center}
\cleardoublepage

